headline: The Estée Lauder Companies’ Oevel Manufacturing & Fulfillment Campus Celebrates 60 Years of Excellence and Innovation
summary: OEVEL, Belgium, October 16, 2025--The Estée Lauder Companies Inc. (NYSE:EL), today celebrated the sixtieth anniversary of its Manufacturing & Fulfillment Campus in Oevel, Belgium. Since its opening in 1965, the Oevel Campus has developed into a state-of-the-art manufacturing, fulfillment and biotech hub.
